{{- /*
~/.terraformrc -- Terraform CLI configuration file.

Rendered by chezmoi to ~/.terraformrc (private mode 0600 because the prefix
on the source filename is `private_dot_`).

Kept deliberately minimal:

  - plugin_cache_dir         shares downloaded providers across every
                             `terraform init` on this host, so a fresh
                             clone doesn't re-fetch hashicorp/aws or
                             every other provider it has seen before.
                             Cuts init time on cold projects from minutes
                             to seconds and saves bandwidth.

  - disable_checkpoint       opt out of HashiCorp's version-check telemetry.
                             We pin versions per-module via `required_version`
                             (see TERRAFORM-01-CORE-STYLE rule), so the
                             check has no upside.

No credentials, no provider mirrors, no plugin overrides. Anything
machine-specific belongs in ~/.terraform.d/credentials.tfrc.json, which
is intentionally NOT chezmoi-managed (it can contain Terraform Cloud /
HCP tokens). Add it to .git-ignored/ if it ends up nearby.
*/ -}}

plugin_cache_dir   = "{{ .chezmoi.homeDir }}/.terraform.d/plugin-cache"
disable_checkpoint = true
